headline: J.B. Hunt Gears Up to Report Q4 Earnings: What's in the Cards?
summary: JBHT's fourth-quarter 2024 revenues are expected to have been weighed down by weakness across most of its segments. Higher net interest expense might have hurt the bottom line.
